The bedroom was fine, usual excellent bedding and linens and the bathroom lovely and spacious with a great rainhead shower; yes, the TV in the bathroom mirror is a gimmick, but we found it entertaining (never seen THAT before)!	The bathroom was amazing - so well designed, massive sunken bath, walk in shower, seperate toilet with it's own glass door, and a tv in the mirror!	The rooms were spotless, and the restaurant food was delicious, beautiful and priced lower than I expected.	The hotel is modern and unlike most Four Season properties, but the rooms were quiet and peaceful.	The room was spotless, and the bed was extremely comfortable.